<div class="container container--narrow" style="padding-top: var(--space-120); padding-bottom: var(--space-120);">
  <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-64);">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  
  <div class="faq-container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    
    <details class="faq-item" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); margin-bottom: var(--space-16); padding-bottom: var(--space-16);">
      <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-size: var(--font-heading-3); outline: none; list-style: none;">
        <span style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
          What is the fit profile of AERIDIAN artifacts?
          <span style="font-size: 24px;">+</span>
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer" style="padding-top: var(--space-16); color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
        Our garments utilize an articulated, anatomical fit. They are drafted to allow maximum kinetic movement without excess volume. We recommend selecting your standard size. For layered systems, our outerwear automatically accommodates our mid-layers.
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); margin-bottom: var(--space-16); padding-bottom: var(--space-16);">
      <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-size: var(--font-heading-3); outline: none; list-style: none;">
        <span style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
          How do I care for proprietary membranes?
          <span style="font-size: 24px;">+</span>
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer" style="padding-top: var(--space-16); color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
        Machine wash cold (30°C) using a technical detergent devoid of enzymes or softeners. Tumble dry on low heat to reactivate the DWR (Durable Water Repellent) finish. Never iron.
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); margin-bottom: var(--space-16); padding-bottom: var(--space-16);">
      <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-size: var(--font-heading-3); outline: none; list-style: none;">
        <span style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
          Do you offer international shipping?
          <span style="font-size: 24px;">+</span>
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer" style="padding-top: var(--space-16); color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
        We dispatch our equipment globally via premium logistics partners. All international orders are shipped DDP (Delivered Duty Paid), ensuring zero friction upon arrival.
      </div>
    </details>

  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ Content",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
